/ (root of repo)
├─ index.html          ← main game hub (grid of game cards)
├─ styles.css
├─ app.js              ← loads games.json, lazy loads iframes
├─ games.json          ← metadata for all 50 games
├─ games/
│   ├─ game-01/
│   │   ├─ index.html
│   │   └─ assets/...
│   ├─ game-02/
│   └─ ...
├─ docs/                ← optional: if you use gh-pages from /docs
└─ README.md
